title: 820-3437 CPU warm
message:
This board seems very clean and has all rails. CPU core - 1.70 but CPU is only a little bit warm. Always used to be hot.
No mouse light.
BIos and lock chip seems very well. Any idea why CPU is not hot?

title: 820-3437 CPU warm
message: Could be anything.....inspect for corrosion, check traces U1900 to Y1905. History?
